            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2026年3月5日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">A股抗跌港夜期彈 高盛籲低吸<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/05/4333343_16774bc2ec9b8a9092f13d65faf1d1c8.png\" title=\"（黃潤根攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/05/4333343_16774bc2ec9b8a9092f13d65faf1d1c8_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/05/4333343_16774bc2ec9b8a9092f13d65faf1d1c8.png\" title=\"（黃潤根攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/03/05/4333343_16774bc2ec9b8a9092f13d65faf1d1c8.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"（黃潤根攝）\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n中東局勢持續緊張，亞太區股市昨幾乎全線下挫，南韓及泰國股市跌幅更觸發熔斷機制。然而，港股及A股跌幅較小，展現較強抗跌力，恒指夜期昨晚更曾反彈逾360點。高盛料全球跌市演變為熊市機會不高，亞股短線市況疲弱是建倉機會，專家則認為現時可分段低吸適當股份。\n亞股全線捱沽 恒指挫2%\n中港股市較區內抗跌力強，...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
